{"id": 1681, "genre": 1001, "title": "游戏、贴吧都要实名制了，你有什么话想说？", "description": "百度将于6月1日起全面实行实名制，《王者荣耀》《阴阳师》等游戏均开启实名制，未实名注册玩家将无法进入游戏。你怎么看！", "record_count": 3036, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201705111104179MqXBVFUA1WToHbK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-11T03:10:00Z", "options": [{"id": 202752, "content": "实名制有利有弊，但应该弊大于利", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980779}, {"id": 202753, "content": "ha", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029359}, {"id": 202754, "content": "能被人用的工具是有价格的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022071}, {"id": 202755, "content": "能知道对方的年龄吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026732}, {"id": 202756, "content": "公权没被关进笼子之前社交网站上的所有实名制都是对言论自由的侵犯", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319710}, {"id": 206852, "content": "和美国聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908163}, {"id": 202757, "content": "反正没见过哪个外国游戏要实名制的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028659}, {"id": 203269, "content": "撤退", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973939}, {"id": 205573, "content": "以后肯定都要实名制", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036171}, {"id": 202758, "content": "个人隐私之殇", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003012}, {"id": 209414, "content": "我在大学时，基本上把所有211.985学校名称当作贴吧号注册了一遍，比如：苏州大学吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880360}, {"id": 205063, "content": "就是不知商家的真是用意", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993269}, {"id": 202760, "content": "无话可说", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029320}, {"id": 205064, "content": "打游戏和实名制有什么关系呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993269}, {"id": 206088, "content": "只能说，去你大爷。实名之后的信息安全没有保障", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037134}, {"id": 207113, "content": "一定要实名制，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039593}, {"id": 202762, "content": "让我们这些社恐怎么活，逛着逛着，“嗨呀，你是不是XXX？我是XXX，记得吧？你也玩这个呀？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015302}, {"id": 203530, "content": "玩游戏本来就是要放松，搞的跟去银行办业务一样就没劲了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031263}, {"id": 202766, "content": "感觉个人信息泄露又多一个途径", "image": "img/option/option/20170511224150UcCRSMKAQeVJq9yr", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997821}, {"id": 202771, "content": "用手机看呗，还能咋看", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945716}, {"id": 204051, "content": "当然好啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1032406}, {"id": 202772, "content": "那我得买个几百T的硬盘来存百度云的东西了", "image": "img/option/option/20170511225546TbEcnlkHuC2opsfi", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628049}, {"id": 202774, "content": "沛公之一不在酒\n司马昭之心昭然若揭", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335521}, {"id": 202775, "content": "如何保证个人信息不外泄", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198246}, {"id": 203287, "content": "我觉得我快要裸露在互联网之中了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1030397}, {"id": 202776, "content": "游戏还行，贴吧实名制？天都要变了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029456}, {"id": 202777, "content": "正好不玩了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974809}, {"id": 202778, "content": "实名制？卵用没有。随便网上一搜找个身份证号一抄", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953682}, {"id": 203290, "content": "有必要吗。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979730}, {"id": 206619, "content": "我就想问贴吧嘛时候能改名", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920963}, {"id": 202780, "content": "无感，反正现在干什么都要身份证，我是不相信他们的保密措施，所以我早就觉得我的身份证号大部分人都知道了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029474}, {"id": 202783, "content": "我完全不介意 很豁达。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68347}, {"id": 203295, "content": "马云哥最大的资本就是掌握了世界百分之几人口的真实信息。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122292}, {"id": 202784, "content": "求推荐好的手机防火墙", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 38243}, {"id": 204577, "content": "支持游戏实名制", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1033348}, {"id": 202786, "content": "我拒绝，不玩了，什么都不玩了(ﾉಥ益ಥ)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007068}, {"id": 202787, "content": "个人信息，将会随处可见。可怕。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010537}, {"id": 202788, "content": "快开启吧我好戒了阴阳师和农药", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964336}, {"id": 202790, "content": "作为一个好公民，我的信息可以被多卖几轮了，想到帮助了那些以卖信息为生的人，我真高兴，以至于睡不着", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804026}, {"id": 203046, "content": "卖片的要被抓？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983451}, {"id": 203302, "content": "我不玩这些游戏，但我不支持实名制。防止未成年人沉迷网络我觉得应该靠全社会共同努力，实名制完全无法制止真正想玩的人吧？而且连玩游戏都有种被盯着的感觉，谁还愿意玩？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1030455}, {"id": 204327, "content": "不玩游戏所以不大有感觉但是贴吧……呵呵呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 63992}, {"id": 203304, "content": "为啥要在六一儿童节做这件扎心的事？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940580}, {"id": 202538, "content": "游戏要实名制，那我应该就是弃坑了要。", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 202539, "content": "只想说赶快，好让我卸了它强制戒断！", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 203307, "content": "不玩了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1030468}, {"id": 204331, "content": "感觉没啥用:  )", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1033322}, {"id": 202540, "content": "“尊敬的家长你们好，这个月内请保管好你们的身份证，因为王者荣耀要实名制了，意味着你家孩子可能会偷拿你们身份证绑定游戏，为了孩子的学习与身心健康，请妥善保管手机和身份证。", "image": null, "praise_count": 682, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 202796, "content": "不玩任何游戏，把网线拔掉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236321}, {"id": 207660, "content": "直接百度上搜一个身份证就可以继续玩了，我不会告诉你们我从小就是这样弄的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040976}]}